WEBVTT

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:02.336
Joseph Jeune also never mentioned
that he was not cost-effective.

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:05.176
A few months of medicines,
and this is what he looked like.

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:07.616
(Applause)

00:11:07.640 --> 00:11:10.136
We call that the Lazarus Effect
of HIV treatment.

00:11:10.160 --> 00:11:12.456
Joseline came to us looking like this.

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:14.736
This is what she looked like
a few months later.

00:11:14.760 --> 00:11:17.456
(Applause)

00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:21.056
Now, our argument, our battle, we thought,

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:25.056
was with the organizations
that kept saying it's not cost-effective.

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:26.496
We were saying, no,

00:11:26.520 --> 00:11:30.416
preferential option for the poor
requires us to raise our aspirations